(15, "IT", "Introduction to Cloud Computing", 3, 3, "NOT_STARTED", NULL, false, NULL, "Even though this course does not require any prior cloud computing or programming experience, by the end of the course, you will have created your own account on IBM Cloud and gained some hands-on experience by provisioning a cloud service and working with it.", 11, 90, STR_TO_DATE("10.12.2022 12:00", "%d.%m.%Y %H:%i"), 30, 60, NULL),
